>Description:
the linear update version of delete, delete! does not work when the element being deleted is the first element in the list. 
>How-To-Repeat:
executing:
(require (lib "1.ss"))
(define ls '(1 2 3))
(delete! 1 ls)
ls

yeilds: 
(2 3) 
(1 2 3)

instead of:
(2 3)
(2 3)
